 usename, password, PII, confidential emails or data
 
 - AWS can be more secure than the on-premise environment
  . Easy encryption
  . Enforcing strong encryption (industry standards) or custom
  . Automate logging and monitoring - Cloud watch/trail
  . Easy audit capabilities - cloud trail
  . AWS inspector to find vulenerabilities
  
  With features of Scaling (scale in and scale out)
  
Clear seggragation of the security responsibilities-

  - Customer: Security "in" the cloud : OS n/w firewall configuration, data...
  - AWS security "of" the cloud : Compute, storage, Database, Networking, AWS global infra
  
  

  
